{"tid":2432673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以眾籌以國安法私人檢控民建聯變革香港","createTime":"2021-03-04T13:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T13:15:02.000Z","uid":17721,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4a256c2645edb7ef68e80e2a99fd2eace72abd1f","tid":2432673,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"變革香港...一聽就知想顛覆國家攻權<br />\n仲要周圍都係banner 開晒記者會<br />\n有無得眾籌請律師檢控<br />\n我實夾一個月糧 <br />\n<br />\n想睇佢地俾保釋之後律政司會唔會上訴"},{"pid":"e28fcb9cb6351ad039a1fef964a3511ee7508c35","tid":2432673,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c62e7f2e0654b11a2534360afdf0d24a7dd2d5e3","tid":2432673,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5bf1a868bfbade10805328286f1662cecd59089d","tid":2432673,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4a56f692b62ef91d1d9623b90bde3a9a840fa3b9","tid":2432673,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"2021年啦"},{"pid":"583304eb03290548d088bca07fef9bfc4cf304e7","tid":2432673,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"國安法冇得私人檢控<br />\n<br />\n第四十一條 <br />\n  未經律政司長書面同意，任何人不得就危害國家安全犯罪案件提出檢控。但該規定不影響就有關犯罪依法逮捕犯罪嫌疑人並將其覊押，也不影響該等犯罪嫌疑人申請保釋。"},{"pid":"5eac8f9601f9c73530108a4baaa4803980d1b5ef","tid":2432673,"uid":262914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"其實點解重會諗用香港既司法制度制衡呢班人?"},{"pid":"b167f0683eb0c7d9b5d48e5015702d5488d1d92a","tid":2432673,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a56f692b62ef91d1d9623b90bde3a9a840fa3b9","tid":2432673,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"2021年啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"20